<section name="322">
	<p>
		He collapses into the gutter, unconscious. After the unpleasant task of searching his body you find, on the <random dice="1">roll of a die</random>:
	</p>
	<outcomes>
		<outcome range="1,2"><item name="lantern"/></outcome>
		<outcome range="3,4"><gain shards="5"/></outcome>
		<outcome range="5,6"><item name="rope"/></outcome>
	</outcomes>
	<p>When you are finished, <goto section="182"/>.</p>
</section>
